name: PhiNesse Eyelash Glue Black
short_description: Longlasting eyelash glue, provides a slight stronger hold while holding the eyelashes securely in place. The dark tone is helping hide the eyelash track in order to enhance the lashline and create the effect of  thicker lashes.
long_description: Longlasting eyelash glue, provides a slight stronger hold while holding the eyelashes securely in place. The dark tone is helping hide the eyelash track in order to enhance the lashline and create the effect of  thicker lashes.
